    <item>
      <title>Version 1.2.0</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        - Apple Intelligence compatibility
        - OCR: Image to text extraction
        - Follow-up conversations with AI
        - Create New Chats to ask AI anything (Cmd+N)
        - Clipboard history improvements (pin, search, up to 100 entries)
        - Shell-compatible custom actions
        - Community extensions (share via YAML, clipboard install)
        - Dark mode improvements
        - UI improvements and bug fixes
      ]]></description>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
